delete, decline, approve, incomplete: -> reload the transaction list and the current transaction view.

submit deliverable: refer figma modal for submit transaction detail.
edit deliverable: it will update the submit modal above. (to prefill the data call "viewDeliverables" api with action "VIEW")

re-submit: exactly like submit, just change the header and api action.

view deliverables: just like edit with disable edit.  add a button for submit feedback.

review feedback: refer figma | disable edit.


